CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1956, pg. 19, reads: "Rough Sparring Mates Rounding Jackson, Baker Into Top Shape - Time for Work - Bob Baker, left photo, and Hurricane Jackson display different emotions as they put on the gloves prior to working out at Rainbow Gardens in preparation for their Sept. 26 bout at Forbes Field. Baker looks like he's taking a quick nap... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Boxer Bob Baker posed with hand on man's shoulders, in boxing ring at Rainbow Gardens, McKeesport
